quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngun fee makko: \"Pellet, oo…óoo ko mbileejo heewu…óo ganndal"
  26,35,Himo faandii yaltinirgol on ka leydi moo…óon mbilewu makko ngun. Ko hun…óun yamir…óon
  26,36,"∆Āe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ca'e …óen moo…ďoo…ďe (mbile)"
  26,37,∆Āe addane kala mbileejo anndu…óo
  26,38,Mbilee…ďe …ďen moo…ďaa fii fodoore √Īalaande anndaande
  26,39,"Yim…ďe …ďen wi'anaa: \"Taw si onon ko on moo…ďike(ndenndi)"
  26,40,"Belajo'o menen men jokkay mbilee…ďe …ďen, si …ďe laatike ko kam…ďe woni foolu…ďe …ďen"
  26,41,"Tuma nde mbilee…ďe …ďen arunoo; …ďe wi'ani Fir'awna: \"Enee, hara no woodani men njo…ďdi si tawii ko men woni foolu…ďe …ďen"
  26,42,"O wi'i : \"Eyyo, haray ontuma on jeyaama e …ďa…ótinaa…ďe …ďen"
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani …ďe: \"mbeddee, ko werloton kon"
  26,44,"∆Āe li…ďi …ďokkoy ma…ď…ďe koy e cawoy ma…ď…ďe kon, …ďe wi'i: \"Sabu teddungal Fir'awna, ko menen woni fooloo…ďe …ďen"
  26,45,"Muusaa werlii tuggordu makko ndun, tawi kayru hindu mo…óa ko …ďe fefindii kon"
  26,46,Mbilee…ďe …ďen suuyi …ďe sujji
  26,47,"∆Āe wi'i : \"Men gom…óinii Jey…óo Winndere nden"
  26,48,Jey…óo Muusaa e Haaruuna
  26,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, on gom…óinay mo, ko adii mi duŇčanaade on? Pellet, ko kanko woni maw…óo moo…óon anndin…óo on on mbilewu ngun, kono aray anndon, mami ta∆īu juu…óe moo…óon e koy…óe moo…óon [ta∆īa] luutindira. Mami fetu on, on fow moo…óon"
  26,50,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Tanaa alaa, menen ko faade ka Joomi amen men ruttotoo"
  26,51,"Menen me…óen tam∆īinii nde Joomi amen yawtani men goopi amen …óin,tawde men laatike adii…ďe gom…óinnde …ďen"
  26,52,"Men Wahayini faade e Muusaa: \"∆äum woni ro∆īidu e jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen. Pellet, onon ko on jokkitetee…ďe"